# Daichi Yoshida

[English](README.md) | [Русский](README.ru.md)

![Daichi Yoshida](image.png)

A free virtual singer with a high, childish and male voice, compatible with UTAU/OpenUTAU only. 

Daichi is a 12 years old kid. Loves tea, singing and his friends. 

## General Information
- Gender: Male
- Species: Human
- Height: 140cm
- Weight: 46kg
- Introduced: 2024
  
## Terms of use
- Commercial Use of Voicebank Allowed: No
- Commercial Use of Character Allowed: No
